⚡️The head of French military intelligence, General Eric Vido, has been dismissed - in part because he failed to anticipate Russia's special operation in Ukraine.  

A military source told CNN that Ukraine was not the only reason; the internal reorganization of the Directorate of Military Intelligence was also poorly judged.   


